ription:<\/strong> The standard model in our lineup, NG EarSafe, offers balanced sound quality with our innovative open-ear design. This model is perfect for everyday use, from listening to music and podcasts to taking calls.<br\/><strong>Applications: <\/strong>Ideal for daily commuters, fitness lovers, and anyone who enjoys background music without losing touch with their environment.<\/p><p><br\/><strong>2. NG EarSafe Comm<br\/><\/strong><br\/><strong>Description:<\/strong> Designed with clear communication in mind, the EarSafe Comm features enhanced microphone clarity making it perfect for professional settings. It integrates noise-cancellation technologies to ensure your calls are crystal clear, even in noisy environments.<br\/><strong>Applications:<\/strong> Best for remote workers, call center employees, and business professionals who need to maintain high-quality communication throughout the day.<\/p><p><br\/><strong>3. NG EarSafe Pro<br\/><\/strong><br\/><strong>Description: <\/strong>The Pro version offers bone conduction technology transmitting sound directly from cheek bones to inner ear via vibrations. It is the only model which works on bone conduction technology being the safest headphones to protect your ears.<br\/><strong>Applications:<\/strong> Suited for people with conductive hearing loss, tech enthusiasts, safe listeners, outdoor enthusiasts.<\/p><p><br\/><strong>4. NG EarSafe Lite<br\/><\/strong><br\/><strong>Description: <\/strong>As the lightest and most affordable option, the EarSafe Lite is designed for casual use, providing basic open-ear listening with a focus on comfort and minimalistic design.<br\/><strong>Applications:<\/strong> Great for individuals who are new to open-ear headphones or those seeking a no-frills audio experience, such as young learners, casual listeners, and active individuals who need lightweight headphones during exercise.<br\/><br\/>Each of these models is tailored to meet specific user needs while maintaining the core benefits of open-ear technology, ensuring everyone can find an NG EarSafe product that fits their lifestyle and listening preferences. Whether for professional use, casual listening, or communication-intensive tasks, NG EarSafe headphones provide a healthier, more comfortable listening experience.<br\/><br\/><strong><br\/>5. NG EarSafe OpenBuds<br\/><\/strong><br\/><strong>Description: <\/strong>The NG EarSafe OpenBuds deliver the ultimate sound experience with our cutting-edge open-ear technology, offering clear and immersive audio without blocking or sealing your ear canals. These true-wireless earbuds combine superior sound quality with the safety and comfort of open-ear design, allowing you to stay aware of your surroundings. With a sleek and portable design, OpenBuds provide the perfect blend of audio excellence and all-day comfort, free from the discomfort or risk of ear canal damage.<br\/><strong>Applications:<\/strong> Ideal for multitaskers, outdoor enthusiasts, and those on the move, OpenBuds are perfect for casual listening, commuting, daily calling because of it's Quad mic and fitness activities, ensuring high-performance sound without compromising awareness or safety.<\/p>","subhd_color":"#222222","hd_color":"#222222","des_color":"#615e5e","use_shadow":false,"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","open_link":"_blank","btn_icon":false,"button_style":"default","btn_size":"large","btn_cl":"dark","button_effect":"default"}}},"block_order":["bl_text_xKeqbF"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center","top_heading":"","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"space_h_item":"20","space_v_item":"10","space_h_item_mb":"20","space_v_item_mb":"10","layout":"t4s-container-wrap","cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,0px,","pd":"50px,,50px,","mg_tb":"","pd_tb":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"image_text_ETT4CN":{"type":"image_text","blocks":{"bl_text_Br4VMY":{"type":"